{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act33side_level_act33side_10_beg","storyGroup":"act33side","storySort":17,"storyDependence":"act33side_level_act33side_09_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BB-10","storyName":"再见，再见","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"特蕾西娅在生命的最后时刻，决定抹除博士的记忆，并在博士漫无边际的记忆中见到了那个意想不到的人。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act33side/level_act33side_10_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act33side_10","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":19,"next":21,"characters":["特蕾西娅","博士"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"charslot","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$ghosthunter_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_ghosthunter_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_bg_49_g10_theresaoffice.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":7},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅很庆幸阿米娅睡着了。","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅没有看见博士的背叛，也没有看见特蕾西娅最后的悲伤。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"在特蕾西娅将议长室中的最后一名刺客抹除的同时，那顶黑色的王冠终于安稳地传递到了阿米娅的手中。","id":12},{"type":"dialog","id":13},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#9$1","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"没事了，阿米娅，没事了......","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"已经结束了。","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":17},{"type":"text","text":"她没有看向那个已经僵直在原地的人，只是轻轻拍了拍怀中孩子的后背，在那张稚嫩的小脸上，落下一吻。","id":18},{"type":"dialog","id":19},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_048","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":20},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......","id":22,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"特蕾西娅。我没办法放弃亿万生命和万年时间才换来的机会。","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我没办法允许你们突破源石的规划。没办法允许你......将这片大地变成一个美好但短暂的梦。","id":24,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#4$1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"所以，你伤害了阿米娅。","id":26,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_048","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......既然魔王已看过了我的记忆，那我们多说无益。","id":29,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"你恨我吗？","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#4$1","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你伤害了阿米娅，你也即将伤害凯尔希，和那些信任你的将士。","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#5$1","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"这是你对待如今这些生命的方式吗？","id":34,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_048","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我会尽全力保证他们不在接下来的冲突中丧命。这也是特雷西斯给我的承诺。","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"只要......你的死亡。","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"......博士，你是出于此刻的愧疚而来到我面前的吗？","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_048","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"比起我所做的事情，愧疚的分量......太轻。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"在凯尔希都不熟知的年代里，我们做出了太多选择。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我只是......","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#10$1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"等阿米娅长大后，若她还记得我，若她问起我，你是否会如实告知她......我是怎样离去？","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4f/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_048","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"不会。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"我会帮助他们寻找另一种生活。","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#10$1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"寻找在源石毁灭泰拉之前最后的安稳？","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4f/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_048","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......抱歉。这无法改变。","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#1$1","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你明知道这是无用功......你却仍旧，想治好阿米娅的病。","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"哪怕在不远的未来，阿米娅的家人、家乡，和你们未来可能建立起联系的那些人和事，都将成为不变的源石。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你也不忍看着眼前的孩子受苦。","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"这是你的真心。是你的纯洁。是你的本性。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_048","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#9$1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我其实......很欣慰，博士。","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我很高兴，凯尔希愿意相信的那个你，愿意相信我们的那个你，是真实存在的。","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你......源石的缔造者......{@nickname}。你是毁去一切的毒，也可以是一切的解药。","id":65,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_048","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"博士","text":"......什么？","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_048.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":68},{"type":"charslot","id":69},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothtrailground","volume":"1","id":70},{"type":"text","text":"看见特蕾西娅强撑着站起，将双手伸向自己，博士本能地想要后退。","id":71},{"type":"text","text":"博士却发现自己的身体无法移动分毫，博士发现自己的悲伤远胜自己强撑的理性。","id":72},{"type":"text","text":"只好任由特蕾西娅触碰面罩之下的面庞。","id":73},{"type":"dialog","id":74},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"你在落泪，博士......","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"是啊，你就是这样的人。你明知道自身的脆弱，明知道哪怕是此时的我，也对你有致命的威胁......你还是来了。","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"所以，我还是......愿意相信你。","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"相信原本的你。","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"相信那个，将雨露和艳阳带给我们的{@nickname}。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_1296_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":81},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_magic_1","volume":"0.5","id":82},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":83},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":84},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","text":"","id":86},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_magic_5","volume":"1","id":87},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":88},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":89},{"type":"charslot","id":90},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":91},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":92},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.5","fillto":"0.15","fadetime":"0.01","id":94},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.5","fillto":"0.15","fadetime":"0.01","id":95},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_bg_49_g10_theresaoffice.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.5","yScale":"1.5","y":"-300","id":96},{"type":"backgroundtween","xFrom":"-100","xTo":"100","duration":"60","ease":"OutQuad","block":"false","id":97},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_048","id":98},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"zoom","poszoom":"0.5,0.5","scale":"1.8","duration":"0","id":99},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"-200,-380","posto":"-100,-380","afrom":"1","ato":"1","duration":"60","id":100},{"type":"bg","id":101,"from":"0","to":"1","duration":"1","block":"false"},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":102},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":103},{"type":"text","text":"这一张脸，既熟悉又陌生。特蕾西娅清楚它的样子。","id":104},{"type":"text","text":"她从未有机会如此直观地从上面捕捉到情绪。","id":105},{"type":"text","text":"她微笑着伸出手指，眼前的景象犹如布匹一般被撕裂开。","id":106},{"type":"text","text":"随后，她缓缓抽出自裂口处松脱的丝线，残余的画面也散解开来，博士的记忆不断消散。","id":107},{"type":"dialog","id":108},{"type":"charslot","duration":"2","id":109},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":110},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_magicwarmthy","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"wa","id":111},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","channel":"wa","fadetime":"2","id":112},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.4","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":113},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":114},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅头也不回地继续深入，继续将每一寸组成博士灵魂的记忆都拆解为一团团苍白混乱的断线。","id":115},{"type":"text","text":"像是很久很久之前的夜晚，幼小的她在特雷西斯身旁自学缝纫那般。","id":116},{"type":"text","text":"记忆消散殆尽，灵魂只剩下了最后一枚碎片。","id":117},{"type":"text","text":"而记忆的尽头处有一个背影。特蕾西娅对那个背影熟悉而又陌生。","id":118},{"type":"text","text":"那是博士，也不是博士。","id":119},{"type":"dialog","id":120},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"1","id":121},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_humanchange","volume":"0.4","id":122},{"type":"delay","time":"0.4","id":123},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.15","fillto":"0","fadetime":"0.5","id":124},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.15","fillto":"0","fadetime":"0.5","id":125},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.4","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":126},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":127},{"type":"charslot","id":128},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_bg_bg_white.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":129},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":130},{"type":"subtitle","text":"<color=#000000>你在对我做什么，特蕾西娅？</color>","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":131},{"type":"subtitle","id":132},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":133},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/dd/Avg_bg_bg_light.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.5","yScale":"1.5","y":"-100","x":"-150","fadetime":"2","id":134},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1296_1#8$1","duration":"2","id":135},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","action":"zoom","poszoom":"0.5,0.5","scale":"1.8","duration":"0","id":136},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"0,-380","posto":"100,-380","duration":"60","id":137},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"虽然已经是最后了，但我突然想卖个关子，你可不要怪我呀，博士。","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"我会对你说......","id":140},{"type":"dialog","id":141},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特蕾西娅","text":"“去找到你自己吧。”","id":143},{"type":"dialog","id":144},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"wa","fadetime":"2","id":145},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":146},{"type":"charslot","id":147},{"type":"background","id":148},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":150},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":151},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":152},{"type":"charslot","id":153},{"type":"background","id":154},{"type":"image","id":155}],"characters":["特蕾西娅","博士"]}